text: Jongile Kilani (born 21 August 1993) is a South African cricketer. He was included in the Border squad for the 2015 Africa T20 Cup. He made his first- class debut for South Western Districts in the 2016–17 Sunfoil 3-Day Cup on 3 November 2016. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:South African cricketers Category:Border cricketers Category:South Western Districts cricketers Category:People from Krugersdorp
